    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> prawn skewers</strong> to the pan with any <strong>remaining garlic, lemon & herb marinade</strong></p><p>Cook for 2-3 min on each side or until the prawns are cooked through – these are your <strong>Mediterranean prawn skewers</strong></p>",
