      "instruction": "<p>Mix the <strong>diced cucumber</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>olives</strong>, <strong>sliced shallot </strong>and<strong> diced tomato </strong>with the<strong> orzo</strong> – this is your<strong> Greek orzo salad</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p>",
