      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Mediterranean prawn skewers</strong> with the<strong> Greek orzo salad</strong> and<strong> salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Crumble your <strong>feta </strong>over the<strong> </strong>Greek orzo salad, and squeeze any<strong> remaining lemon juice </strong>over the salad</p><p>Season everything with a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Got a BBQ? Grab the plates and fire up the barbie. This recipe is a grill’s best friend.</span></strong></p>",
